Class PropertiesDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dhemery.configuring.PropertiesDictionary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StringDictionary

    public class PropertiesDictionary
extends Object
implements StringDictionary
    A dictionary stored in a Properties. Changes to the dictionary are written through to the underlying properties. Properties in the underlying properties are reflected in the dictionary
